org.gvsig.installer.maven

Class GeneratePluginPackageSetMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractMojo
      • org.gvsig.installer.maven.AbstractGeneratePackageMojo
        • org.gvsig.installer.maven.GeneratePluginPackageSetMojo

  • public class GeneratePluginPackageSetMojo
extends AbstractGeneratePackageMojo
    Maven mojo to launch the gvSIG installer to generate a installation bundle of a gvSIG plugin.

    Look at the gvSIG plugin naming standard for information about installers naming and versioning.

    See Also:
    InstallerManager
